{
  "total_duration": 695.809,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 10.76,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你吃完饭，准备付钱，突然发现包不见了。你会紧张吗？当然会。因为没有包，就可能没有钱包，也就不能"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pay the bill"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 11.11,
      "end": 23.885,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He often does this!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文是“他经常干这种事！”这里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "he"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是人，而是一只调皮的狗。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 24.235,
      "end": 42.443,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先把旧场景接到现在。课文里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "village pub"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是现代城市夜店，也不是只喝酒的地方。在这个故事里，它更像英国乡村里的小餐馆加社区空间：可以吃午饭，老板也熟悉这里的人和动物。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 42.793,
      "end": 61.06,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "landlord"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里也不是收房租的房东，而是经营这家"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pub"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的人，也就是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pub owner"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "或"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "manager"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "bill"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是吃完饭要付的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "meal bill"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 61.41,
      "end": 72.41,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以这篇故事不是惊险偷窃，而是一个轻松误会：客人以为包丢了，付不了饭钱；老板却笑了，因为他知道，那只狗又把东西叼到花园里去了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 72.76,
      "end": 85.64,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天要抓住这条链："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "missing thing, worry, explanation, familiar habit, relief"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。东西不见了，先紧张；知道原因以后，才发现只是熟悉的小麻烦。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 85.99,
      "end": 99.853,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一帧，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在一个温暖的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "village pub"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "吃完午饭。课文第一句说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "After I had had lunch at a village pub, I looked for my bag."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 100.203,
      "end": 116.143,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "注意这里有两个"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。第一个"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "帮助组成"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "past perfect"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，第二个"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had lunch"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“吃午饭”。先吃完午饭，后来才开始找包。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 116.492,
      "end": 125.468,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "记得很清楚："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I had left it on a chair beside the door."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他之前把包放在门边的椅子上。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 125.818,
      "end": 133.61,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二帧，问题来了。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "and now it wasn't there!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "包现在不在那里了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 133.96,
      "end": 145.159,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他正在找包的时候，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "landlord"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "进来了，问："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Did you have a good meal?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这是一句很普通的饭后问候：吃得好吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 145.509,
      "end": 158.789,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "很尴尬地回答："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Yes, thank you, but I can't pay the bill. I haven't got my bag."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他不是想赖账，而是真的没有包，没法付饭钱。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 159.139,
      "end": 167.275,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三帧，最有意思的反应出现了。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The landlord smiled and immediately went out."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 167.625,
      "end": 180.193,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "如果是陌生地方，老板可能会紧张。可是这个"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "landlord smiled"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。他笑了，不是因为客人倒霉，而是因为他大概已经猜到发生了什么。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 180.542,
      "end": 192.678,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "immediately"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是马上、立刻。他没有审问客人，也没有报警，而是直接往外走，很可能是去"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "garden"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "找答案。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 193.028,
      "end": 206.372,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四帧，答案揭晓。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "In a few minutes he returned with my bag and gave it back to me."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "几分钟后，他拿着包回来了，并把包还给"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 206.722,
      "end": 215.354,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后他说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I'm very sorry. My dog had taken it into the garden. He often does this!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 215.703,
      "end": 225.055,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "我们在学生侧把这句读成"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "My dog had taken it into the garden."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为意思很清楚：狗把包叼到花园里去了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 225.405,
      "end": 241.153,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "标题的笑点就在这里："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He often does this!"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "来说是一次小惊吓；对"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "landlord"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "来说，是家里那只狗又干了熟悉的小坏事。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 241.503,
      "end": 254.142,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这篇课文最容易误会两个地方。第一，把"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pub"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "想成夜店；第二，把故事想成"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "theft"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，偷窃。其实都不是。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 254.492,
      "end": 258.202,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pub"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "到底是什么？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 258.551,
      "end": 272.055,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这篇课文里，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a village pub"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是英国乡村里可以吃饭、聊天、见邻居的小地方。它可以卖饮料，但故事重点不是喝酒，而是吃完午饭要付账。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 272.405,
      "end": 275.755,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "landlord"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是房东吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 276.105,
      "end": 294.84,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "很多时候是房东，但在"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pub"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "里，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "landlord"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "指经营"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pub"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的人，也就是老板或经理。所以"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the landlord came in"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pub owner"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "走进来了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 295.19,
      "end": 300.761,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不能"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pay the bill"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 301.111,
      "end": 313.831,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为他说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I haven't got my bag."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这是英式日常说法，意思是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I don't have my bag with me"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。没有包，就没法付"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "meal bill"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 314.181,
      "end": 318.642,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "landlord"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "smiled"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 318.992,
      "end": 333.787,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为他熟悉自己的狗。别人看到"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "missing bag"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "会"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "worry"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "；他看到这个情况，会想到"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "familiar habit"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "：狗经常把东西叼到"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "garden"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 334.137,
      "end": 336.062,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以狗是坏狗吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 336.412,
      "end": 348.116,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是。这里的狗"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "playful"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，不是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "criminal"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。它没有偷钱，也没有制造危险，只是把包当成有趣的东西搬走了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 348.466,
      "end": 352.642,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "After I had had lunch at a village pub, I looked for my bag."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 352.991,
      "end": 357.359,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I had left it on a chair beside the door and now it wasn't there!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 357.709,
      "end": 361.141,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "As I was looking for it, the landlord came in."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 361.491,
      "end": 365.571,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Did you have a good meal? he asked."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 365.921,
      "end": 369.833,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Yes, thank you, I answered, but I can't pay the bill."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 370.183,
      "end": 372.487,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I haven't got my bag."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
